3d45f17ecb8904ba7242c776c84a53f84d966c51.query:
select 
                ty."program", 
                count(*) as "count!", 
                count(ty.note) as "note_count!"
            from public.ty 
            group by ty."program"
            order by "count!" desc
            limit 200;

5ca401f6925a5a1eba36760d82c065fcb1569f55.query:
select ty.note as "note!"
            from public.ty 
            where ty.note is not null
                and ty.program = $1
            limit 200;
